TextEng: You are a madman, that much is clear.
Text: 당신은 미친 사람이군요, 그건 분명해 보입니다.

TextEng: Are you Quint Jhareg?
Why do the undead walk these halls?
Text: 왜 언데드들이 이 복도를 걷고 있나요?

TextEng: Didn't we meet before?
Be at peace. I come as the Judge.
You be Mister Quint, yuh?
We meet before?
No, me be da Judge-guy.
Why there so many undead here?
Hmm. You no make much sense.
Text: 흠. 너 말 이해 안 돼.

TextEng: Tell me more...
Get to the point.
Yuh? Ooh, you keep talking...
You got point? Get to it.
Tell me more...
Get to the point.
Yuh? Ooh, you keep talking...
You got point? Get to it.
Will you give that as a written oath?
I've spoken to Karlat. He tells a different story.
Text: 칼랏과 얘기했습니다. 그는 다른 이야기를 하던데요.

TextEng: This your journal?
I still have some questions.
You gives that as written oath?
Me talk to Karlat already. His story different.
Text: 나 칼랏이랑 얘기했어. 그 사람 다른 말했어.

TextEng: Me still have questions.
What role did your brother play in this?
Text: 당신 형제는 이 일에서 어떤 역할을 했나요?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> You seem eager to confess...
Do you know what a phylactery is?
What Judgment do you long for?
What your brother do in all this?
Text: 너 형은 이 일에서 뭐 했어?

TextEng: What is this philacta-thingy?
What be da Judgment you wanting?
All right, enough questions.
Okay, 'nuff questions, yuh?
You loved the children.
You thought it was going to be a party.
Text: 당신은 그게 파티가 될 거라고 생각했군요.

TextEng: You said your brother was acting strangely.
Text: 당신은 형제가 이상하게 행동하고 있다고 말했군요.

TextEng: You're right, it doesn't say anything.
You loved da children, yuh?
You thought it was for big party.
Text: 너 그게 큰 파티인 줄 알았어.

TextEng: You said Karlat act funny.
Yuh, that's right. It not say anythin' important...
That's all it said. Will you give that as a written oath?
Text: 그게 전부입니다. 그걸 서면 맹세로 해주시겠습니까?

TextEng: Uh, that's all it said. You gives that as written oath?
Text: 어, 그게 전부야. 서면 맹세로 해줘?

TextEng: Could you excuse me for a moment?
Uh... me be right back, 'kay?
